/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
23 January 2024	navcs2	ChangeRequest 57088: EUP | Correct Info on Departed Transport for Itemized Cargo
10 October 2025	navcs2	MTN-36215 The removed quantity for the cargo item is not displayed in the Details section of the Vehicle Visit Enquiry form.
13.10.25	Navcs2	MTN-36202	MTN | Invoice Form displaying empty rows when rows are added from Selector form

*/

vars

begin
	// 10 October 2025	navcs2	MTN-36215  Start
	if self.mnuTblColumnOrganiser.userObject = self.tblOnsiteTrackedItems then					// 13.10.25	Navcs2	MTN-36202
		self.tblOnsiteTrackedItems.showColumnOrganiserFrm(self.myTerminal,null);
	else
		self.tblReleasedTrackedItems.showColumnOrganiserFrm(self.myTerminal,null);
	endif;
	// 10 October 2025	navcs2	MTN-36215  End
epilog

end;</source>
